{
  "texts": [
    "Quality assessment revealed a majority of studies at high risk of bias.",
    "The meta-analysis showed a pooled accuracy of 57% (95% CI: 51-63%) for generative AI models.",
    "Physicians generally outperformed AI models, although in non-expert settings, some AI models showed comparable performance.",
    "Our analysis also highlighted significant differences in effectiveness across medical fields.",
    "To the best of our knowledge, this is the first meta-analysis of generative AI models in diagnostic tasks."
  ]
}